Preconditions:
- The `bottom` string must not be null or empty.
- The `allowed` list must not be null or empty.
- The `allowed` list must contain at least one element.

Postconditions:
- The method returns `true` if it is possible to build the pyramid all the way to the top using the given `bottom` and `allowed` list.
- The method returns `false` if it is not possible to build the pyramid all the way to the top using the given `bottom` and `allowed` list.